5.title: Clip: Police Patrol Boat

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds City - Artifex (TV Series 2014– )

5.plot: Keep the crook from escaping his boat ride to prison. Toss the crook in the Police Patrol Boat's holding cell and start the cruise to Prison Island to drop him off. Watch out, another crook has pulled alongside and is trying to break the prisoner out of the cell with the getaway boat's anchor. Can you stop them escaping and bring the crooks to justice? Lego 60129.

6.title: Clip: Police Tow Truck Trouble

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds City - Artifex (TV Series 2014– )

6.plot: Be part of the action with the Lego City police as they race after the crook trying to tow away a safe. Lego 60137.

7.title: Clip: Police High-Speed Chase

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds City - Artifex (TV Series 2014– )

7.plot: Be part of the action with the Lego City police as they call in Chase McCain to help stop the crook escaping with the loot in the stolen sports car. Lego 60138.

8.title: Clip: Police Money Transporter

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds City - Artifex (TV Series 2014– )

8.plot: Be part of the action with the Lego City police as the officer stops the crook from getting away with the safes. Lego 60142.

9.title: Clip: Arctic Base Camp

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds City - Artifex (TV Series 2014– )

9.plot: Plan and go on the ultimate expedition from Lego City Arctic Base Camp. Head out into the wilds and set up the hi-tech Lego City Arctic Base Camp to explore the secrets of the ice. Set out on major expeditions with the snow scooter and husky sled team. Investigate the secrets of the ice with the powerful tracked exploration vehicle. Lego 60036.

10.title: Clip: Jungle Cargo Helicopter

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds City - Artifex (TV Series 2014– )

10.plot: Head deep into the Lego City jungle with the Jungle Explorer Helicopter, featuring an opening mini-figure cockpit, spinning rotors and working winch, an A.T.V with space for a mini-figure, a treasure box and a temple with moving leaf revealing a gold-colored chalice. Lego 60158.

11.title: Clip: Jungle Halftrack Mission

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds City - Artifex (TV Series 2014– )

11.plot: Explore what lies within the Lego City jungle on a Jungle Halftrack Mission, featuring a truck with tracks on the back wheels, storage space for the chain and tool elements, plus an ATV with removable crate, a buildable campfire and a buildable temple with diamond element and moveable stone that releases a spider. Lego 60159.

12.title: Clip: Coast Guard Sea Rescue Plane

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds City - Artifex (TV Series 2014– )

12.plot: Be part of the brave crew of the Lego City coast guard in the Sea Rescue Plane, featuring spinning propellers, an opening cockpit, lowering back ramp and space for the included rescue water scooter, plus a rescue raft and rescue light. Lego 60164.

13.title: Clip: Coast Cuarg 4 x 4 Response Unit

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds City - Artifex (TV Series 2014– )

13.plot: Join the rough and ready crew of the Lego City coast guard and their 4x4 Response Unit, featuring a 4x4 truck with opening mini-figure cab, opening rear compartment with space for tools and gear, and a detachable trailer for the included rescue craft with room for 2 mini-figures, drop-down engines and spinning propellers, radio antennas, toolbox and life preservers. Lego 60165.

14.title: Clip: Jungle Air Drop Helicopter

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds City - Artifex (TV Series 2014– )

14.plot: Haul in fresh supplies at the exploration site. Gear up to tackle the Lego City jungle with the Jungle Air Drop Helicopter. Use the work tower crane to unload the pallet transporter from the riverboat, and then haul a load of supplies out to the site with the clamp system on the helicopter. Hop behind the wheel of the 4x4 truck to pull the temple statue upright and look behind it. Lego 60162.

15.title: Clip: Coast Guard Sailboat Rescue

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds City - Artifex (TV Series 2014– )

15.plot: Gear up the rescue craft and get ready for action. Take a call from a stranded sailor out on a rocky island, hop in the rescue craft and race off. Keep an eye out for the shark as you get closer to the boat. Fly deep into the Lego City jungle and make a cool discovery with this Lego City Jungle Cargo Helicopter 60158 Set.

imdb.plot outline: Lego City is a realistic Lego world for your child to explore. Iconic vehicles and buildings form the backdrop to this bustling city, with everyday heroes catching bad guys and putting out fires. This is a world full of humor and charm that will really stimulate their creative imaginations.
